L,NULL,15000,1,'liuyuan_config_20260601','liuyuan_config_20260601','2026-06-01 17:03:06.033','2026-06-01 19:59:44.046'),(329,59,1,'TEXT','','','收到作业啦～ 今天的课程上的怎么样？学习一定是要坚持并且长期学习下去的，不能够半途而废哦，我先听听咱们这次提交的情况哈',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,2000,1,'liuyuan_config_20260601','liuyuan_config_20260601','2026-06-01 17:03:06.368','2026-06-01 19:59:44.046'),(330,59,2,'VOICE','','',NULL,'https://kkhc.tos-cn-beijing.volces.com/eps-juzibot/permanent/material/%36%61%31%64%34%61%63%61%61%61%61%30%64%30%66%34%65%32%36%30%35%61%66%34.silk','https://drh.likeduoduiyi.cn/homework/voice/876a2e6b159f49b1852dfbe8bd511f35.mp3',20000,NULL,NULL,20000,1,'liuyuan_config_20260601','liuyuan_config_20260601','2026-06-01 17:03:07.728','2026-06-01 19:59:44.046'),(331,60,1,'TEXT','','','今天是倒数第二节课了！您依然很用心的在跟着我学习，我先听听您的作业',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,2000,1,'liuyuan_config_20260601','liuyuan_config_20260601','2026-06-01 17:03:08.069','2026-06-01 19:59:44.046'),(332,60,2,'VOICE','','',NULL,'https://kkhc.tos-cn-beijing.volces.com/eps-juzibot/permanent/material/%36%61%31%64%34%61%63%63%61%30%36%37%63%30%66%64%37%39%35%62%39%32%32%33.silk','https://drh.likeduoduiyi.cn/homework/voice/a597df3e73994ae2a13b5874544c9000.mp3',17000,NULL,NULL,17000,1,'liuyuan_config_20260601','liuyuan_config_20260601','2026-06-01 17:03:09.452','2026-06-01 19:59:44.046'),(333,61,1,'TEXT','','','好嘞同学！今天是最后一天一起学习啦，我听完你的作业了，您听听',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,2000,1,'liuyuan_config_20260601','liuyuan_config_20260601','2026-06-01 17:03:09.826','2026-06-01 19:59:44.046'),(334,61,2,'VOICE','','',NULL,'https://kkhc.tos-cn-beijing.volces.com/eps-juzibot/permanent/material/%36%61%31%64%34%61%63%65%61%61%61%30%64%30%66%34%65%32%36%30%35%63%62%33.silk','https://drh.likeduoduiyi.cn/homework/voice/fa169a3e176a4378b0fe976eb8c8965f.mp3',17000,NULL,NULL,17000,1,'liuyuan_config_20260601','liuyuan_config_20260601','2026-06-01 17:03:11.105','2026-06-01 19:59:44.046'),(335,62,1,'TEXT','','','我听完了！确实是有在勤加练习，特别好学！我也很开心能够遇到勤奋的同学，相信您这样坚持勤练下去，咱们一起能学有所成！',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,2000,1,'liuyuan_config_20260601','liuyuan_config_20260601','2026-06-01 17:03:11.433','2026-06-01 19:59:44.046'),(336,63,1,'TEXT','','','嗯！能修正一些细节上的唱法，很不错，喉咙一定要打开、放开、让声音出来，换气的时候要大口吸气，慢慢吐出来，这样就能让气息越来越稳！',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,2000,1,'liuyuan_config_20260601','liuyuan_config_20260601','2026-06-01 17:03:11.801','2026-06-01 19:59:44.046'),(337,64,1,'TEXT','','','这一次稍微好很多了，气的感觉已经上来了，剩下的就是稳住，您要是有时间，多看看第二节课的回放，把咱们气息的运用多巩固巩固，这样以后唱高音就更没问题啦！',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,2000,1,'liuyuan_config_20260601','liuyuan_config_20260601','2026-06-01 17:03:12.211','2026-06-01 19:59:44.046'),(338,65,1,'TEXT','','','才开始可以不用着急去抓节拍和节奏，先跟着自己拍掌的频率来唱，这样就能够掌握的更好！',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,2000,1,'liuyuan_config_20260601','liuyuan_config_20260601','2026-06-01 17:03:12.607','2026-06-01 19:59:44.046');
